{"tid":930612,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"選項黐隱線","createTime":"2018-12-06T12:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T12:15:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1c02d53824755543210af8b3109d7308bf0237","tid":930612,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20181206/20561945\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181206%2F20561945&d=BK1g1eN8jI%2B4p8cgbZaFdPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=dc706f18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181206%2F20561945&h=15ee06aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20181206/20561945</a><br />\n<br />\n選項黐隱線 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20181206/large/1544000176_8de0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20181206%2Flarge%2F1544000176_8de0.jpg&h=8355e38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n「加油」被編入牛津字典，市民對入津無乜太大feel。<br />\n<br />\n其實香港本土已經夠材料，可以自己編輯一套後傘運詞典。像近期最鬼扯的，「港獨是不是選項」，是最「萬能key」的官方封殺借口，子彈都慳返，選項，已有罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傘運後，「DQ」執行了N次，使用率之高，是潮語之冠。將來有機會以DQ清袋取代一Q清袋，書迷等住村上春樹寫包膠的DQ84吧。<br />\n<br />\n「選舉主任」本來很難入典，但近年曝光率極高，反面人氣排公務員第二，僅次「黑警」。<br />\n<br />\n不久將來，跟明日大嶼同步，法官都可以炒魷，由選舉主任兼職。主任大人，是咁的，市民信納你好on9，憐憫做人做到你咁柒，確係百年牛津不遇。<br />\n<br />\n「紅線」，請勿超越。港鐵四線會一齊仆，就係因為條黃線未轉紅。<br />\n<br />\n「搬龍門」已成極權常態，個波明明射入了白界，黑哨判你入球無效。還叫人「射票落海」？<br />\n<br />\n講呢啲，黐隱線！  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n不方便麵 (楊靜)"}]}